lead_paragraph: THE REVIEW YESTERDAY.--The military parade, yesterday, was the best and most imposing we have ever seen in Brooklyn, affording a display of citizen soldiery as creditable to our city as it was attractive and gratifying to the people, in point of discipline and general appearance.
